# Dashboard Enhancements Implementation Plan

This plan outlines the steps to add bulk selection, confirmation modals, a finance dashboard, and persistent notifications.

## Proposed Changes

### [Backend] Persistence & Notifications
- [NEW] `backend/src/routes/notifications.ts`: Routes for managing notifications.
- [MODIFY] [backend/src/routes/bookings.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/backend/src/routes/bookings.ts): Insert record into `notifications` when a booking is created.
- [MODIFY] [backend/src/routes/messages.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/backend/src/routes/messages.ts): Insert record into `notifications` when a message is created.
- [MODIFY] [backend/src/index.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/backend/src/index.ts): Register notifications route.

### [Frontend] Core Components
- [NEW] `frontend/src/components/dashboard/ConfirmModal.tsx`: A reusable modal for destructive actions.

### [Frontend] Dashbaord State
- [NEW] `frontend/src/store/slices/notificationsSlice.ts`: State management for persistent notifications.
- [MODIFY] [frontend/src/store/store.ts](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/store/store.ts): Add `notificationsSlice` to the store.

### [Frontend] Feature Pages
- [MODIFY] [frontend/src/app/dashboard/bookings/page.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/bookings/page.tsx): 
    - Add multi-selection logic.
    - Integrate `ConfirmModal` for deletion.
- [MODIFY] [frontend/src/app/dashboard/vehicles/all/page.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/app/dashboard/vehicles/all/page.tsx):
    - Integrate `ConfirmModal` for deletion.
- [NEW] `frontend/src/app/dashboard/finance/page.tsx`:
    - Financial charts and metrics.
    - PDF export functionality.

### [Frontend] Layout & Navigation
- [MODIFY] [frontend/src/components/dashboard/Header.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/components/dashboard/Header.tsx):
    - Display 5 notifications max.
    - Persistence logic (fetch from API instead of Redux state).
    - "See previous" pagination/scroll.
- [MODIFY] [frontend/src/components/dashboard/AppSidebar.tsx](file:///d:/car%20rental%20landing%20page/frontend/src/components/dashboard/AppSidebar.tsx):
    - Add "Finance" link to the nav menu.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Manual Testing

### Manual Verification
1.  **Selection**: Toggle "Select All" in bookings, verify all checkboxes reflect state.
2.  **Confirmation**: Click delete on a booking, verify modal appears, then confirm delete.
3.  **Finance**: Navigate to /dashboard/finance, verify charts load, click "PDF Export" and check result.
4.  **Notifications**: Create a new booking, see it in notifications. Delete the booking, verify notification remains. Click notification bell, see only 5 items. Click "See previous", verify more items load.
